Plain sentence:
---------------
    Maintaining the integrity of the power grid is one of those topics that make your eyes glaze over--until the power grid
    collapses and the lights go out, as it did for much of Virginia after Hurricane Isabel in 2003, and then it becomes
    all-consuming.

